LANG_ENGLISH        "I thought you were going to get me out of here?"
LANG_CZECH        "Myslel jsem, ze me odsud dostanes?"

REFERENCE           10LAC019
LANG_ENGLISH        "Whatever you tried didn't work. I'm still stuck in here."
LANG_CZECH        "Cokoliv jsi zkusil, nepomohlo to. Porad tu trcim."

